  "id": "019d33ed-515b-7632-9cb6-441e93f0e6ea",
  "content": "# Multi-Spoke Design: Complete (2026-03-28)\n\nAll review fixes incorporated into main design docs. Design is implementation-ready.\n\n## Final Documents\n1. `2026-03-28-multi-spoke-workspace-brainstorm.md` - Architecture, decisions, PoC results\n2. `2026-03-28-spoke-cli-design.md` - CLI commands, HubContext, entrypoint, Dockerfile, test plan\n3. `2026-03-28-spoke-dashboard-design.md` - AgentsView enhancement, Docker graceful degradation\n4. `2026-03-28-spoke-design-review-summary.md` - 5-persona review audit trail\n5. `2026-03-28-spoke-design-review-fixes.md` - Review fixes audit trail (incorporated)\n\n## Key Changes from Review\n- MCP bearer token auth on writes\n- Per-spoke cryptographic agent tokens\n- Non-root containers, pinned Claude Code version\n- Resource limits (4GB default), log rotation\n- Pre-flight validation, startup health gate, error reporting\n- Deterministic network selection\n- Container detection check\n- Test plan with unit/integration/E2E/negative/platform matrix\n- Telemetry for audit log, metrics, spoke log capture (not corvia_write)\n\nReady for GitHub issues and implementation.",
